Word
Purpose: Represents a single word in the scripture and whether it is hidden.
Responsibilities:

Store the text of the word

Track whether the word is hidden

Hide itself when asked

Display either the real word or blanks

------------------------------
|            Word            |
------------------------------
| - _text : string           |
| - _isHidden : bool         |
------------------------------
| + Word(text)               |
| + Hide()                   |
| + IsHidden() : bool        |
| + GetDisplayText() : string|
------------------------------





